title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x86 en-US September 2015
description:
*************************************************************
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x86 en-US September 2015 
*************************************************************

Office Professional 2013 was designed to help you create and communicate faster, with time-saving features and a clean, modern look across all your programs. Plus, save your documents online in OneDrive to access virtually anywhere.

The 32-bit version of Office is recommended for most users, because it's more compatible with most other applications, especially third-party add-ins.
Read more: https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ee681792.aspx

Included applications: Word 2013, Excel 2013, PowerPoint 2013, OneNote 2013, Outlook 2013, Publisher 2013, Access 2013, InfoPath 2013, Skype for Business 2015

System requirements:

- Processor: 1 gigahertz (Ghz) or faster x86-bit processor with SSE2 instruction set
- Operating System: Windows 8.1, Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Server 2008 R2, or Windows Server 2012
- Memory: 1GB RAM (32 bit)
- Disk Space: 3.0GB available
- Display: Graphics hardware acceleration requires a DirectX 10 graphics card and 1024 x 576 resolution
- .NET Version: 3.5, 4.0, or 4.5

Release Info:

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Includes SP1 and KB files until 30 September 2015
- File: ProPlus15.X86.en-US-2015.09.iso
- Size: 2.33 GB
